    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于”狙击枪”套装</h2><br>特殊武器系列都有独特动画，战争前线的玩家都喜欢 - 终于在Steam上架了。无限力量就是在你的手中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/d13edddbc7b5142fe7bedd26938f0a0a.poster.avif?t=1685625895\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/d13edddbc7b5142fe7bedd26938f0a0a.webm?t=1685625895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/d13edddbc7b5142fe7bedd26938f0a0a.mp4?t=1685625895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>武器要中有传奇武器，每一把武器能够给你带来胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/7f879a4e87c320300401b93d5ad522bd.poster.avif?t=1685625895\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/7f879a4e87c320300401b93d5ad522bd.webm?t=1685625895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/7f879a4e87c320300401b93d5ad522bd.mp4?t=1685625895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>系列中有8种武器，都合适多样的战斗情况！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SAI GRY AR-15 &quot;辛迪加&quot;</h2>SAI GRY AR-15 的的现代化版本，配有双弹鼓、符合人体工程学的突击手握把和抑制器。这把武器优秀合适任何战斗情况，任何距离。武器具有高伤害，此外也可以给肢体造成额外伤害。武器容量较大，射击速度不快不慢，正合适。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/bc47c343d951635cb7c268a1ac98e57b.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Saiga H.G.C. Custom &quot;辛迪加&quot;</h2>Saiga 是一把 12 号口径的战斗霰弹枪，支持各类改装。和卡拉什尼科夫步枪的改型一样，这是一把滚转式枪击、弹匣供弹的导气式武器。武器射击速度很快，伤害很大，很合适面对许多敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/e1a5741f1f9136a633b7419673ead4d8.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >H&amp;K MP5A5 Custom &quot;辛迪加&quot;</h2>H&amp;K MP5 采用了 MP5 冲锋枪的经典配置，后者出自德国小型军火制造商黑克勒&amp;科赫 (H&amp;K) 公司之手。这把武器拥有舒适的后坐力、极佳的变焦速度和高超的伤害，足以在近距离下将敌人爆头。近和中距离种这种武器一定不让你的敌人避免死亡！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/bc47c343d951635cb7c268a1ac98e57b.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AT308 &quot;辛迪加&quot;</h2>AT308继承了经过战斗洗礼的遗产，将其带上了一个新高度。AT308 有一个固定枪托和 不少 英尺长的快装平整枪管。是执法单位和民用的不二之选。武器距离很好，特殊子弹能够给敌人造成更多伤害。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/80ff6e43a58eefca49c185ebf7bdd637.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beretta ARX160 &quot;辛迪加&quot;</h2>Beretta ARX160 是一种独特突击步枪。这把武器的特色包括适度的后坐力、高射速以及能对四肢造成额外伤害或在远距离造成额外伤害的重型穿甲子弹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/3d8d4a3198844a0489df1f94cbee1a56.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fabarm XLR5 Prestige &quot;辛迪加&quot;</h2>Fabarm XLR 5 Prestige 不只拥有出色的火力，还有炫酷的视觉设计。由 Fabarm 武器公司制造的这把武器得到了广泛的应用，出现在诸如狩猎、自卫和攻击中等多种场合。武器容量时7个子弹，也可以一个一个换弹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/dc87d9c3730576a078f798c49b87f7f9.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Micro-Roni &quot;辛迪加&quot;</h2>Micro RONI 是最新型号的手枪-驳壳枪转换器，也是手枪-卡宾枪转换套件的最新紧凑型产品，即由铝和高分子聚合物打造的轻盈、坚固的格洛克手枪和普通手枪平台。武器容量时60个子弹，腰射精度优秀！武器配有折叠功能和可调整尼龙支架，可以提供更稳定的固定。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/53f78f88633b94339bd432f14f772bf2.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remington MSR &quot;辛迪加&quot;</h2>雷明顿 MSR 是一款轻铝材质手动栓式狙击步枪，武器表示模块化狙击步枪，因为该武器可通过切换枪管和枪栓实现 .多样口径快速切换。这是一款现代化的精准步枪，就是价格有点昂贵。武器具有两种配件：4x瞄准镜Bushnell和Remington MSR灭火器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/fc55b230bc4759bbbe6984467a695169.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>理所当然玩家可以通过使用这些武器来得到更多成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753610/extras/7cad671fc48c2b03b93611794ad24381.avif?t=1685625895\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>支付好之后请稍等15分钟左右。如果物品还没到账的话，请重新启动游戏。",
